{
  "stem": "24163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, there were those that were in the higher hierarchies of the Social Democrats, the Catholic party, and what have you, certainly, the Communist party, who was-- who were arrested, who were arrested by-- by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I am sure-- I assure you that, in the beginning, Dachau was a camp for political prisoners, as much or more so than it was for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all in the camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And many of them died and got killed there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And among them, there was some-- some religious leaders-- some religious leaders.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so that's what I said, some of them became Nazis, and others were deported by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was immediately sent to a camp outside of Amsterdam first.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was only for about a week or so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was sort of like a transit camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, they sent us to youth hostels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One, if I'm not mistaken, was near the city of Utrecht.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other was near the city of Deventer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there, we lived a very comfortable life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We could work in the fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had strawberries and other vegetables out in the fields.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We worked in the fields.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of us worked in carpenter shops that were in these youth hostels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We worked, but we did the kind of work that would not interfere [CLEARS THROAT] with the economy of Holland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We could not get a job, so to speak, and-- and work officially in Holland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We would have to work within the youth hostels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents, they were waiting very, very patiently, from that moment on, until the end of 1939, for their visa, for their number to come through at the German consulate in Stuttgart, Germany.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And towards the end of 1939, they finally called them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
